    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like a loop. i wake up, i try to pretend things are fine, then i remember everything i've lost and i just want to sleep for a year. like, what's the actual goal here? i'm just running in place until i break. i honestly just want the noise to stop. i just want peace.",
